        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A graviton crystal increases the forces of gravity around your solar manifestations, accelerating its impact and possibly trapping foes within its gravity field. While graviton attuned, your solar weapon or solar flare deals an extra @Damage[1d6[untyped]] damage of your solar weapon's or flare's damage type. On a critical hit while you're graviton attuned, the target must succeed at a @Check[fortitude|dc:31] save or be @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for 2 rounds.</p>\n<p>Additionally, when you hit an immobilized or suppressed creature with your solar weapon or solar flare, the target must succeed at a @Check[fortitude|dc:31] save or be knocked prone.</p>"
